      <title>在3月审判的Openai大修时进行的Musk-Altman摊牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/musk-altman-showdown-over-openai-overhaul-set-for-march-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官在埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）对山姆·阿尔特曼（Sam Altman）计划彻底改革Openai的业务结构的计划中进行了三月审判，为两位亿万富翁之间的高风险冲突奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/musk-altman-showdown-over-openai-overhaul-set-for-march-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 22:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
